  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Combine your<strong> soy sauce </strong>with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> in a large bowl – this is your <strong>'bacon' flavouring</strong></p><p>Trim the<strong> </strong>stalk[s] off your <strong>aubergine[s]</strong> and cut in half lengthways</p><p>Slice each half, lengthways, as finely as you can (approx. 0.5cm in thickness)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1588587874860-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1588587874860-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1588587874860-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1588587874860-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1588587874860-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> aubergine slices</strong> to the <strong>'bacon' flavouring</strong> and give everything a good mix up until the aubergine is fully coated (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with<strong> non-stick baking paper</strong>, add the <strong>coated aubergine</strong> and put the tray[s] in the oven for 30-35 min or until starting to crisp – this is your <strong>smoky aubergine</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
