            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>potato[es] </strong>(skin on) into wedges</p><p>Add the<strong> wedges </strong>to a separate baking tray with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min, or until cooked through and golden</p>",
